title: ICICI Prudential AMC Set to Launch $1.2 Billion IPO on Dec. 12
description: India’s ICICI Prudential Asset Management Co. is seeking a valuation of as much as 1.07 trillion rupees ($11.9 billion), calculations by Bloomberg showed, as it plans to launch its initial public offering on Dec. 12.
